What's Here:
============

queue
-----

A basic client server sample with an implementation of ZMQ_QUEUE using zmq_reactor.

pair
----

A small program that demonstrates zmq_reactor_pair.


req_server
----------

Client-server app demonstrating server threads using a ZMQ_REQ socket

=============

NB There are no makefiles (yet) because I'm building this on a Mac, so you really don't want my xcodeproj file :-)
